{"tid":677012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回應特朗普取消峰會　朝鮮：隨時願與美國會談","createTime":"2018-05-24T23:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T02:45:18.000Z","uid":53379,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b7b9146a214aacb24d05c89dfe335407df57441a","tid":677012,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T23:31:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">回應特朗普取消峰會　朝鮮：隨時願與美國會談</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n當朝鮮周四(24日)按承諾廢棄核試場之際，美國總統特朗普突然表示取消下月12日在新加坡舉行的美朝峰會；朝鮮在數小時後回應稱，平壤仍然願意和美國在任何時候、以任何形式面對面會談解決問題，又稱最高領導人金正恩為美朝峰會全力以赴做準備。<br />\n<br />\n國營朝鮮中央通訊社發布副外相金桂冠的聲明稱，美國單方面決定取消即將舉行的美朝峰會，顯示雙方之間的敵意仍然嚴重，也正好反映兩國之間峰會的急切需要。金桂冠強調朝鮮為世界和朝鮮半島和平及穩定努力的承諾不變，亦以開放態度給予美國時間和機會。<br />\n<br />\n(韓聯社)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180525/s00005/1527204446951\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180525%2Fs00005%2F1527204446951&d=8P8rv8oVU7T5x%2FhCmoa3YfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=09b291f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180525%2Fs00005%2F1527204446951&h=3b1eeb72\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180525/s00005/1527204446951</a>"},{"pid":"7b83d9e45f4e9f76e1e8cc7cc50a567db68bd470","tid":677012,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T23:34:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f4bf44a9de90031017bca007626faabd2cf807e","tid":677012,"uid":22701,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T23:38:38.000Z","msg":"擺明玩大左淆底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894afa7737f7945b5e4c1433286f6dd70664276d","tid":677012,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T23:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cacec6dcdd6281092793